<div class="content" style="color: #333;">
  <h1 style="color: #f8cdd6; text-align: center;">Your Reservation has been Canceled</h1>
  <p>Dear <strong><%= @user.first_name %> <%= @user.last_name %></strong>,</p>
  <p>This is to confirm that your reservation at Sakura Stay has been canceled. If you have any questions or need further assistance, feel free to reach out to us.</p>
  <p>Here are the details of the canceled reservation:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Room:</strong> <%= @reservation.room.name %></li>
    <li><strong>Check-in Date:</strong> <%= @reservation.check_in_date.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></li>
    <li><strong>Check-out Date:</strong> <%= @reservation.check_out_date.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></li>
  </ul>
  <p>If you have any questions or need further assistance, feel free to contact our support team.</p>
  <p>Best regards,</p>
  <p>The Sakura Stay Team</p>
  <p style="text-align: center;">
    <a href="mailto:support@sakurastay.com" class="btn" style="color: #ffffff; background-color: #333333; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;">Contact Support</a>
  </p>
</div>
